data.description: SHORE ACRES COTTAGE! Embrace the opportunity to call this Shore Acres Cottage your home, only a few minutes drive from the heart of Downtown St. Petersburg. Downtown offers an array of esteemed dining establishments, some of the best museums in the state, and is home to the newly renovated St. Petersburg Pier. Revel in the convenience of strolling across the street to enjoy the brand-new Shore Acres Recreation Center. This home is graced with an expansive layout that seamlessly integrates a welcoming living room, a cozy movie theatre, and a kitchen designed for entertaining. The kitchen has unique stainless steel counter tops, ALL NEW SAMSUNG APPLIANCES and lots of storage. Step into the future with this “Family Hub” Wi-Fi and Bixby enabled refrigerator. Explore beyond your movie theatre and home office and you will find your owner’s suite oasis, where you'll find an abundance of natural light and a rejuvenating ensuite bathroom. The walk-in closet and bath are hidden behind custom sliding “barn doors” on the reclaimed wood accent wall. A true split floorplan, on the other side of your home you will find two spacious bedrooms that also boast natural light, fear not, there is also a second bathroom on this side of your new home! Noteworthy features such as the greenhouse off of the kitchen, a custom-built tiki-bar perfect for entertaining (because it's 5 o'clock somewhere!), a firepit to keep you warm during our chilly Florida winters, or simply to enjoy s'mores around, continue exploring around your new backyard and you will find that there is plenty of storage around back as well. OFFERED FURNISHED, this is the perfect move-in ready home, no matter if this will be your year-round or seasonal home or an investment property that can be leased right away, without any additional investment. CALL TODAY BEFORE THIS BEAUTY SAILS INTO THE SUNSET WITHOUT YOU!
